videoDetails.Title: Desmos Easter Eggs
videoDetails.Description:
Haha, I managed to get an extra video this month by doing a #shorts
Desmos Easter Eggs in shorts

When typing betchacant in a desmos graph will cause it to redirect to one of 8 graphs.
Typing Pride redirects to graphs with the pride flag
putting ?plaidMode at the end of the url of a graph causes it to change coloring of shapes.

Desmos Discord: https://discord.gg/TgtCtjxQb2

Original reddit post: https://www.reddit.com/r/desmos/comments/i2s354/i_bet_you_cant/

Music- Megaman Soccer Wood Field

This video, although only 53 seconds long, took 6 hours to edit. So please subscribe, or comment, a hello in the comments section will make me very happy.

#desmos
